## <a id="prerequisites"></a>Prerequisites

To complete installation of Altoros Log Search for Pivotal Platform, you need the following:

* CPU, RAM, and disk resources for 11 VMs for shared service plan
* Internet connectivity between the networks where the Pivotal Platform deployment and Log Search are installed. Altoros recommends installing Log Search on the same network with Pivotal Platform.

